extends layout

block content
  // Begin Page Content 
  .container-fluid
    // Page Heading 
    .d-sm-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-between.mb-4
      h1.h3.mb-0.text-gray-800 Home
    .row
      .col-lg-6
        // Basic Card Example 
        .card.shadow.mb-4
          .card-header.py-3
            h6.m-0.font-weight-bold.text-primary Calculus & Analysis
          .card-body
            p Compute integrals, derivatives and limits as well as analyze sums, products and series.
            p
              | Compute an integral:
              br
              b integrate sin x dx from x=0 to pi
            p
              | Calculate a derivative:
              br
              b derivative of x^4 sin x
            p
              | Solve an ordinary differential equation:
              br
              b y'' + y = 0
        // Basic Card Example 
        .card.shadow.mb-4
          .card-header.py-3
            h6.m-0.font-weight-bold.text-primary Differential Equations
          .card-body
            p Solve differential equations of any order. Examine solutions and plots of the solution families. Specify initial conditions to find exact solutions.
            p
              | Solve a linear ordinary differential equation:
              br
              b y'' + y = 0
            p
              | Specify initial values:
              br
              b y'' + y = 0, y(0)=2, y'(0)=1
            p
              | Solve a nonlinear equation:
              br
              b f'(t) = f(t)^2 + 1
      .col-lg-6
        // Basic Card Example 
        .card.shadow.mb-4
          .card-header.py-3
            h6.m-0.font-weight-bold.text-primary Applied Mathematics
          .card-body
            p Perform numerical analysis and optimization of systems and objects, including packing and covering of objects and control systems.
            p
              | Minimize or maximize a function:
              br
              b maximize x(1-x)e^x
            p
              | Numerically integrate functions that cannot be integrated symbolically:
              br
              b integrate sin(cos x) from x=0 to 1
            p
              | Minimize or maximize a function subject to a constraint:
              br
              b maximize e^x sin y on x^2+y^2=1
        // Basic Card Example 
        .card.shadow.mb-4
          .card-header.py-3
            h6.m-0.font-weight-bold.text-primary Algebra
          .card-body
            p Find roots of and expand, factor or simplify mathematical expressionsâ€”everything from polynomials to fields and groups.
            p
              | Solve an equation:
              br
              b x^3 - 4x^2 + 6x - 24 = 0
            p
              | Factor a polynomial:
              br
              b factor 2x^5 - 19x^4 + 58x^3 - 67x^2 + 56x - 48
            p
              | Simplify an expression:
              br
              b 1/(1+sqrt(2))
